events.name: San Antonio Spurs at Indiana Pacers

headlines.description: — Coby White scored 24 points, and the Chicago Bulls used a big third quarter to pull away for a 120-100 win over the short-handed Houston Rockets on Monday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Coby White scores 24, Bulls hand Rockets 8th straight loss

events.name: Miami Heat at Oklahoma City Thunder

headlines.description: — Duncan Robinson scored 22 points and made six 3-pointers, leading the Miami Heat to a 108-94 victory over the Oklahoma City Thunder on Monday night in the finale of their seven-game road trip.
headlines.shortLinkText: Heat pull away to beat Thunder 108-94 in finale of road trip

events.name: Portland Trail Blazers at Phoenix Suns

headlines.description: — Devin Booker scored 34 points, Deandre Ayton added 19 and the Phoenix Suns kept rolling with a 132-100 win over the Portland Trail Blazers on Monday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Booker scores 34, Suns roll to 132-100 win over Blazers

headlines.description: — Donovan Mitchell had 23 points and eight assists as the Utah Jazz enjoyed a record-breaking performance from long range in a 132-110 victory over the Charlotte Hornets on Monday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Jazz set records for 3s in 132-110 rout of Hornets

events.name: Washington Wizards at Los Angeles Lakers

headlines.description: — Bradley Beal scored six of his 33 points on three consecutive possessions late in overtime, and the Washington Wizards extended their longest winning streak in three years to five straight with a 127-124 victory over the slumping Los Angeles Lakers...
headlines.shortLinkText: Wizards win 5th straight, hold off Lakers 127-124 in OT
